'''伊斯蘭國控制地區人權'''，泛指[[恐怖主義|恐怖主義]]組織[[伊斯蘭國|伊斯蘭國]]控制地區下的[[人權|人權]]狀況。

== 一般公民权利 ==
=== 新聞自由 ===
伊斯蘭國控制地區的[[新聞工作者|新聞工作者]]必須先效忠該組織才能從事新聞工作，他們在攝影和公開圖片前須經伊斯蘭國同意，經常遭受不同形式的惡劣對待<ref name=news>{{cite news |author1=Rana Sabbagh |title=Syria: Inside the World’s Deadliest Place for Journalists |url=http://gijn.org/2014/12/03/syria-inside-the-worlds-deadliest-place-for-journalists/ |accessdate=2015-10-10 |agency=Global Investigative Journalism Network |date=2014-12-03 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151010155627/http://gijn.org/2014/12/03/syria-inside-the-worlds-deadliest-place-for-journalists/ |archivedate=2015-10-10 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。如果伊斯蘭國控制地區有新聞工作者受雇於反對伊斯蘭國的組織，他們的攝影器材會遭到沒收；如果新聞工作者不遵從伊斯蘭國的指示的話，他們會被拘禁入獄、遭到[[鞭刑|鞭刑]]或被殺<ref name=news/>。一些身處伊斯蘭國控制地區的專業新聞工作者會在網上發佈新聞報導，「[[拉卡正無聲地被屠宰|拉卡正無聲地被屠宰]]」便是其中一例<ref name=news/>。

伊斯蘭國曾多次襲擊新聞工作者，並企圖奪取其控制地區內的傳媒設施<ref>{{cite news |title=Report: Press freedom experienced 'drastic decline' in 2014 |url=http://america.aljazeera.com/articles/2015/2/12/report-press-freedom-experienced-drastic-decline-in-2014.html |accessdate=2015-10-10 |agency=Al Jazeera America |date=2015-02-12 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150214163024/http://america.aljazeera.com/articles/2015/2/12/report-press-freedom-experienced-drastic-decline-in-2014.html |archivedate=2015-02-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。[[無國界記者|無國界記者]]指出，伊斯蘭國意圖掌控[[新聞|新聞]]和[[資訊|資訊]]，針對不宣傳{{link-en|伊斯蘭國意識形態|Ideology of the Islamic State of Iraq and the Levant}}的新聞從業員；伊斯蘭國被無國界記者形容為「新聞自由在[[伊拉克|伊拉克]]和[[敘利亞|敘利亞]]遭受的最大威脅」<ref>{{cite news |title=ISIS – MAJOR THREAT TO MEDIA FREEDOM IN BOTH IRAQ AND SYRIA |url=http://en.rsf.org/iraq-isis-major-threat-to-media-freedom-30-12-2013,45680.html |accessdate=2015-10-10 |agency=Reporters Without Borders |date=2013-12-30 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151010161746/http://en.rsf.org/iraq-isis-major-threat-to-media-freedom-30-12-2013,45680.html |archivedate=2015-10-10 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

=== 宗教自由 ===
伊斯蘭國被指在其控制地區內殺害和[[歧視|歧視]][[基督教徒|基督教徒]]，這些措施包括：禁止基督教徒受雇於{{link-en|公營部門|Public sector}}、破壞[[基督教|基督教]]的建築物和其他文物、要求基督教徒繳納其他民眾不用繳交的特殊[[稅項|稅項]]、強迫患病或殘疾的基督教徒改信[[伊斯蘭教|伊斯蘭教]]，以至驅逐或[[屠殺|屠殺]]控制地區內的基督教徒<ref name=religion>{{cite web |author1=Tom Malinowski |title=ISIL's Persecution of Religious Minorities in Iraq and Syria |url=http://www.state.gov/j/drl/rls/rm/2014/231483.htm |website=U.S. Department of State |accessdate=2015-10-10 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151010173648/http://www.state.gov/j/drl/rls/rm/2014/231483.htm |archivedate=2015-10-10 |deadurl=yes |date=2014-09-10 }}</ref>。大量居於伊斯蘭國控制地區的基督徒逃離家鄉，但他們逃難時可能會被武裝份子截停，財物亦遭到沒收<ref>{{cite news |author1=Victor Beattie |title=US, UN Denounce ISIL Persecution of Iraqi Minorities |url=http://www.voanews.com/content/us-un-denounce-isil-persecuriton-of-iraqi-minorities/1962569.html |accessdate=2015-10-11 |agency=VOANews.com |date=2014-07-22 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151011013105/http://www.voanews.com/content/us-un-denounce-isil-persecuriton-of-iraqi-minorities/1962569.html |archivedate=2015-10-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。伊斯蘭國武裝份子曾在[[利比亞|利比亞]][[綁架|綁架]]21名信奉基督教的[[埃及|埃及]]勞工，先迫令其[[下跪|下跪]]，再把他們[[斬首|斬首]]<ref>{{cite news |title=Islamic State: Egyptian Christians held in Libya 'killed' |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-31481797 |accessdate=2015-10-11 |agency=BBC |date=2015-02-15 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150216000227/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-31481797 |archivedate=2015-02-16 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

除了基督徒外，[[雅茲迪|雅茲迪]]教徒也{{link-en|伊斯蘭國對雅茲迪教徒的迫害|Persecution of Yazidis by ISIL|受伊斯蘭國迫害}}，迫害手法包括綁架、[[人口販運|人口販運]]、驅逐、[[酷刑|酷刑]]及殺害等<ref name=religion/>。伊斯蘭國亦迫害其控制地區內的[[什葉派|什葉派]][[穆斯林|穆斯林]]；該組織認為，什葉派的穆斯林是[[叛教|叛教]]者，要使伊斯蘭教純潔，就必須讓他們全部死去<ref>{{cite news |author1=ALISSA J. RUBIN |title=Questions Rebels Use to Tell Sunni From Shiite |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/06/25/world/middleeast/questioning-helps-rebels-tell-sunnis-from-shiites.html?_r=0 |accessdate=2015-10-11 |agency=The New York Times |date=2014-06-24 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20140903190411/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/06/25/world/middleeast/questioning-helps-rebels-tell-sunnis-from-shiites.html?_r=0 |archivedate=2014-09-03 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。伊斯蘭國有神職人員在[[佈道|佈道]]時表示，什葉派穆斯林是伊斯蘭教的敵人，又聲言要「在[[真主|真主]]的旨意下」，像宰殺[[羊隻|羊隻]]般殺害他們<ref>{{cite news |author1=ROBERT SPENCER |title=ISIS Muslim cleric tells Shia: "Allah willing, we shall slaughter you like sheep" |url=http://www.jihadwatch.org/2015/07/isis-muslim-cleric-tells-shia-allah-willing-we-shall-slaughter-you-like-sheep |accessdate=2015-10-11 |agency=Jihad Watch |date=2015-07-23 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151011014436/http://www.jihadwatch.org/2015/07/isis-muslim-cleric-tells-shia-allah-willing-we-shall-slaughter-you-like-sheep |archivedate=2015-10-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

=== 死刑及酷刑 ===
在伊斯蘭國控制地區下，犯下[[謀殺|謀殺]]、[[同性戀|同性戀]]行為、[[叛教|叛教]]或[[褻瀆|褻瀆]]的人可被處[[死刑|死刑]]，謀財害命者可被[[釘十字架|釘十字架]]處死，已婚[[通姦|通姦]]者可被處以[[石刑|石刑]]<ref name=crimes/>。伊斯蘭國處決犯人的手法還包括斬首、[[火刑|火刑]]、[[溺死|溺死]]犯人、炸死犯人等<ref>{{cite web |author1=Ted |title=LEAKED VIDEO: ISIS Puts Innocent People In A Giant Cage, Locks Them Inside, Sinks Them Into A Pool And Drowns Them To Death. They Then Take Another Group Of People, Wrap Them With Explosive Rope And Blow Them Up To Pieces |url=http://shoebat.com/2015/06/23/leaked-video-isis-puts-innocent-people-in-a-giant-cage-locks-them-inside-sinks-them-into-a-pool-and-drowns-them-to-death-they-then-take-another-group-of-people-wrap-them-with-explosive-rope-and-b/ |website=Walid Shoebat |accessdate=2015-10-11 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151011053439/http://shoebat.com/2015/06/23/leaked-video-isis-puts-innocent-people-in-a-giant-cage-locks-them-inside-sinks-them-into-a-pool-and-drowns-them-to-death-they-then-take-another-group-of-people-wrap-them-with-explosive-rope-and-b/ |archivedate=2015-10-11 |deadurl=no |date=2015-06-23 }}</ref>。伊斯蘭國亦在其控制地區使用酷刑，在當地[[婚前性行為|婚前性行為]]、[[誹謗|誹謗]]和[[飲酒|飲酒]]者可遭到[[鞭刑|鞭刑]]，[[盜竊|盜竊]]和[[搶劫|搶劫]]者可被迫令[[截肢|截肢]]<ref name=crimes>{{cite news |author1=Mary Atkinson |author2=Rori Donaghy |title=Crime and punishment: Islamic State vs Saudi Arabia |url=http://www.middleeasteye.net/news/crime-and-punishment-islamic-state-vs-saudi-arabia-1588245666 |accessdate=2015-10-11 |agency=Middle East Eye |date=2015-01-20 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150204073439/http://www.middleeasteye.net/news/crime-and-punishment-islamic-state-vs-saudi-arabia-1588245666 |archivedate=2015-02-04 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，在公共場所未配戴標準面紗的婦女可能被潑[[硫酸|硫酸]]毀容。伊斯蘭國拘禁下獄的犯人亦遭到酷刑對待，例如[[電擊|電擊]]、[[毆打|毆打]]和鞭刑等<ref>{{cite web|title=RULE OF FEAR: ISIS ABUSES IN DETENTION IN NORTHERN SYRIA|url=https://www.amnesty.org/download/Documents/16000/mde240632013en.pdf|website=Amnesty International|accessdate=2015-10-11|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150704125758/http://www.amnesty.org/download/Documents/16000/mde240632013en.pdf|archivedate=2015-07-04|deadurl=no|date=2013-12-19}}</ref>。

伊斯蘭國視[[吸煙|吸煙]]為犯罪，曾對吸煙者施以斬首和鞭刑的刑罰；有煙民被發現在伊斯蘭國控制地區內吸煙，因而遭到酷刑對待，手指被武裝份子以[[鉗子|鉗子]]掰斷<ref>{{cite news |author1=SAMUEL SMITH |title=劊子手被斬首：ISIS主要警員被砍頭 疑因吸煙 |url=http://chinese.christianpost.com/article/%E5%8A%8A%E5%AD%90%E6%89%8B%E8%A2%AB%E6%96%AC%E9%A6%96-isis%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E7%96%91%E5%9B%A0%E5%90%B8%E7%85%99%E8%A2%AB%E7%A0%8D%E9%A0%AD-18847/ |accessdate=2015-12-05 |agency=基督郵報 |date=2015-01-06 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151205083220/http://chinese.christianpost.com/article/%E5%8A%8A%E5%AD%90%E6%89%8B%E8%A2%AB%E6%96%AC%E9%A6%96-isis%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E7%96%91%E5%9B%A0%E5%90%B8%E7%85%99%E8%A2%AB%E7%A0%8D%E9%A0%AD-18847/ |archivedate=2015-12-05 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

=== 食物權 ===
伊斯蘭國控制下的敘利亞在2015年上半年出現[[小麥|小麥]]短缺問題，當地的[[農民|農民]]受武裝衝突、[[燃料|燃料]]不足、氣候欠佳等問題困擾；農民投訴指，伊斯蘭國沒有支援農民耕作，又沒有像敘利亞政府這樣向他們採購莊稼，令農民要尋找新買家，期間經常遭到中間人欺騙<ref>{{cite news |author1=Maggie Fick |title=ISIS-Controlled Iraq Is Looking At A Wheat Shortage |url=http://www.businessinsider.com/r-special-report-for-islamic-state-wheat-season-sows-seeds-of-discontent-2015-1 |accessdate=2015-10-11 |agency=Business Insider |date=2015-01-20 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151011113318/http://uk.businessinsider.com/r-special-report-for-islamic-state-wheat-season-sows-seeds-of-discontent-2015-1?r=US&IR=T |archivedate=2015-10-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

=== 衛生保健權 ===
伊斯蘭國在其宣傳影片中介紹了類似[[英國國民保健署|英國國民保健署]]、名為「伊斯蘭國保健署」的[[衛生保健|衛生保健]]服務，片中有多名身穿醫生服男子接受訪問，又聲稱伊斯蘭國有來自[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]、[[突尼斯|突尼斯]]、[[斯里蘭卡|斯里蘭卡]]和[[澳洲|澳洲]]的醫生，也有女性醫療人員；該段宣傳影片指，伊斯蘭國控制地區不欠缺醫療設施，但缺乏人手，故請求外國人前來當地<ref>{{cite news |title=Isis mimics Britain's NHS with 'Islamic State Health Service ISHS' |url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/isis-mimics-britains-nhs-islamic-state-health-service-ishs-1498183 |accessdate=2015-10-11 |agency=IBTimes UK |date=2015-04-24 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151011120255/http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/isis-mimics-britains-nhs-islamic-state-health-service-ishs-1498183 |archivedate=2015-10-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=ISIS Health Care Video An Ad For A Welfare State |url=http://www.vocativ.com/usa/nat-sec/isis-health-care-video-an-ad-for-a-welfare-state/ |accessdate=2015-10-11 |agency=Vocativ |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151011120355/http://www.vocativ.com/usa/nat-sec/isis-health-care-video-an-ad-for-a-welfare-state/ |archivedate=2015-10-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。另一方面，伊斯蘭國控制下的伊拉克面臨衛生情況惡化，當地衛生保健服務崩潰，[[食水|食水]]受到污染，[[藥品|藥品]]短缺，[[疥瘡|疥瘡]]、[[利甚曼病|利甚曼病]]等疾病盛行<ref>{{cite web |title=ISIS-held Iraq plagued by health problems |url=http://www.scidev.net/global/conflict/news/isis-iraq-plagued-health-problems.html |website=SciDev.Net |accessdate=2015-10-11 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151011121305/http://www.scidev.net/global/conflict/news/isis-iraq-plagued-health-problems.html |archivedate=2015-10-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

== 特定人群的權利 ==
=== LGBT權利 ===
[[伊斯蘭國|伊斯蘭國]]被指涉嫌迫害[[同性戀者|同性戀者]]和[[變性人|變性人]]，該組織聲稱處決了至少30名涉嫌[[雞姦|雞姦]]者，亦有男同性戀者遭到伊斯蘭國{{link-en|法外處決|Extrajudicial killing}}<ref>{{cite news |title=ISIL persecutes gay, lesbian, trans people, experts tell UN |url=http://america.aljazeera.com/articles/2015/8/24/isil-executed-30-people-for-sodomy-un-meeting-told.html |accessdate=2015-10-11 |agency=Al Jazeera America |date=2015-08-24 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151011063201/http://america.aljazeera.com/articles/2015/8/24/isil-executed-30-people-for-sodomy-un-meeting-told.html |archivedate=2015-10-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。伊斯蘭國武裝份子曾把兩名同性戀者從一座大廈的[[天台_(建築物)|天台]]拋到地面，他們最終被群眾扔石殺害<ref>{{cite news |author1=Sam Prince |title=WATCH: ISIS Throws 2 ‘Gay Men’ Off Roof & Stones Them |url=http://heavy.com/news/2015/08/new-isis-islamic-state-video-but-who-is-better-than-god-in-judgment-establishing-a-limit-upon-the-people-homs-syria-gay-homosexual-man-executed-executed-uncensored-full-youtube-video/ |accessdate=2015-10-11 |agency=Heavy |date=2015-08-14 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151011063235/http://heavy.com/news/2015/08/new-isis-islamic-state-video-but-who-is-better-than-god-in-judgment-establishing-a-limit-upon-the-people-homs-syria-gay-homosexual-man-executed-executed-uncensored-full-youtube-video/ |archivedate=2015-10-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。敘利亞和伊拉克均有同性戀者逃離家鄉，以防因[[性取向|性取向]]而遭受迫害<ref>{{cite web |author1=Michael Borger |title=Why is ISIL the herald of LGBT rights? |url=http://www.gradedtalon.com/3614/showcase/why-is-isil-the-herald-of-lgbt-rights/ |website=The Talon |accessdate=2015-10-11 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151011064208/http://www.gradedtalon.com/3614/showcase/why-is-isil-the-herald-of-lgbt-rights/ |archivedate=2015-10-11 |deadurl=no |date=2015-10-01 }}</ref>。

=== 殘疾人人權 ===
伊斯蘭國武裝份子曾虐待和殺害[[身心障礙者|身心障礙者]]，令一些殘疾人被迫逃走<ref>{{cite news |author1=HERMOINE MACURA |title=Iraqis Fleeing ISIS Reveal Horrors of Militants Abusing, Killing Disabled People (Interview) |url=http://www.christianpost.com/news/special-needs-survivors-testify-of-islamic-state-fighters-killing-disabled-people-141816/ |accessdate=2015-10-11 |agency=The Christian Post |date=2015-07-23 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151011110102/http://www.christianpost.com/news/special-needs-survivors-testify-of-islamic-state-fighters-killing-disabled-people-141816/ |archivedate=2015-10-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。一名無辜的[[心理疾病|心理疾病]]患者在伊斯蘭國控制地區遭到武裝份子的訊問，他因患病而情緒失控，[[掌摑|掌摑]]一名武裝份子；該患者其後被伊斯蘭國武裝份子[[槍斃|槍斃]]，武裝份子阻止民眾拯救他，令他{{link-en|失血致死|Exsanguination}}<ref>{{cite news |author1=TOM WYKE |title=Mentally ill man is shot dead by ISIS after his condition ‘forced him to lose control’ and slap Islamic State guard as the men argued |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2992965/ISIS-brutally-murder-mentally-disabled-man-burn-death-55-year-old-woman-not-paying-taxes-Syria.html |accessdate=2015-10-11 |agency=Daily Mail Online |date=2015-03-13 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151011111320/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2992965/ISIS-brutally-murder-mentally-disabled-man-burn-death-55-year-old-woman-not-paying-taxes-Syria.html |archivedate=2015-10-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

=== 婦女權益 ===
一份由伊斯蘭國轄下組織[[坎莎旅|坎莎旅]]發佈的文件顯示，伊斯蘭國反對[[男女平等|男女平等]]和{{link-en|女性教育|Female education}}，該組織認為婦女只能負責家庭事務，只可在特殊情況下離家，而她們的工作時數亦遭到限制<ref name=marrige>{{cite news |title=揭開ISIS女子軍團的神秘面紗 |url=http://beyondnewsnet.com/20150210-demystifying-isis-woman-legion/ |accessdate=2015-10-11 |agency=超越新聞網 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151011074356/http://beyondnewsnet.com/20150210-demystifying-isis-woman-legion/ |archivedate=2015-10-11 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。坎莎旅是伊斯蘭國控制地區的女性武裝組織，負責管制市內的婦女，檢查她們的衣着是否符合規範<ref name=VICE>{{cite news |author1=Alice Speri |title=Raqqa Is Being Slaughtered Silently, And These Guys Are Risking Their Lives To Document It |url=https://news.vice.com/article/raqqa-is-being-slaughtered-silently-and-these-guys-are-risking-their-lives-to-document-it |accessdate=2015-10-09 |agency=VICE News |date=2014-09-26 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20140926054845/https://news.vice.com/article/raqqa-is-being-slaughtered-silently-and-these-guys-are-risking-their-lives-to-document-it |archivedate=2014-09-26 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，以及管理淪為[[性奴隸|性奴隸]]的雅茲迪女子；有婦女因[[公開哺乳|公開哺乳]]、[[尼卡布|尼卡布]]太透明等「罪名」而遭坎莎旅成員施以酷刑，武裝份子以帶有尖刺的夹子夹傷她們的[[乳房|乳房]]，令受刑婦女的乳房完全損毀<ref>{{cite news |title=叙妇公开哺乳 遭IS「乳刑」伺候 |url=http://dailynews.sina.com/gb/news/int/chinesedaily/20141231/06036350314.html |accessdate=2015-10-11 |agency=中国日报 |date=2014-12-31 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151011074641/http://dailynews.sina.com/gb/news/int/chinesedaily/20141231/06036350314.html |archivedate=2015-10-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

在[[婚姻|婚姻]]方面，伊斯蘭國允許九歲以上的女孩結婚，又認為大部分女性的適婚年齡均在17歲前<ref name=marrige/>；有些父親強迫他們的女兒嫁給伊斯蘭國武裝份子，這些被[[迫婚|迫婚]]的婦女有的自殺，有的在被迫出嫁後遭到[[性暴力|性暴力]]<ref name=VICE/>。伊斯蘭國涉及[[強姦|強姦]]、{{link-en|强制引产|Forced abortion}}和買賣女奴等[[對婦女的暴力行為|針對女性的暴力]]，而伊斯蘭國控制地區內亦有雅茲迪女子被充當貨物，可供販賣、購買和餽贈<ref name=CNN>{{cite news |author1=Atika Shubert |author2=Bharati Naik |title=ISIS soldiers told to rape women 'to make them Muslim' |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2015/10/08/middleeast/isis-rape-theology-soldiers-rape-women-to-make-them-muslim/ |accessdate=2015-10-11 |agency=CNN |date=2015-10-08 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151011081552/http://edition.cnn.com/2015/10/08/middleeast/isis-rape-theology-soldiers-rape-women-to-make-them-muslim/ |archivedate=2015-10-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。有武裝份子聲稱，強姦婦女的行為可以令她們變成穆斯林<ref name=CNN/>；有武裝份子在強姦時向受害者表示，此舉可以令自己和真主更親近，而伊斯蘭教也允許強姦不信者<ref>{{cite news |author=SAM WEBB |title=ISIS told Yazidi sex slaves that rape is part of their twisted corruption of Islam |url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/isis-told-yazidi-sex-slaves-6251415 |accessdate=2015-10-11 |agency=Mirror Online |date=2015-08-14 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151011082205/http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/isis-told-yazidi-sex-slaves-6251415 |archivedate=2015-10-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

=== 兒童權利 ===
伊斯蘭國控制地區下的家長為利益而把他們的孩童送到該組織的訓練營，這些孩童在營內學習《[[古蘭經|古蘭經]]》和[[武術|武術]]，並被[[教化|教化]]成為[[吉哈德|吉哈德]]份子<ref>{{cite news |author1=Tom Porter |title=Isis pays parents for children to attend jihadist 'cub' camps |url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/isis-pays-parents-children-attend-jihadist-cub-camps-1489911 |accessdate=2015-10-11 |agency=IBTimes UK |date=2015-02-28 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151011090458/http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/isis-pays-parents-children-attend-jihadist-cub-camps-1489911 |archivedate=2015-10-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。最少120名大部分為雅茲迪教徒的男童遭到伊斯蘭國綁架，被迫進入該組織的訓練營，學習成為吉哈德份子，他們要觀看斬首的影片，再用[[玩偶|玩偶]]練習斬首技術；這些孩童被教導要[[仇恨|仇恨]]他人，他們在營內遭到武裝份子的威脅和虐打<ref name=beaten>{{cite news |title=ISIS teaches children beheading techniques on dolls |url=https://www.rt.com/news/310397-isis-children-behead-dolls/ |accessdate=2015-10-11 |agency=RT |date=2015-07-21 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151011092319/https://www.rt.com/news/310397-isis-children-behead-dolls/ |archivedate=2015-10-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。伊斯蘭國的宣傳影片曾出現小童親自殺害敘利亞士兵的情節<ref name=beaten/>，更有小童在影片中聲言要把[[美國總統|美國總統]][[奧巴馬|奧巴馬]]斬首<ref>{{cite news |author1=Nicole Rojas |title=Isis: Child jihadi threatens to behead President Obama in latest propaganda video |url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/isis-child-jihadi-threatens-behead-president-obama-latest-propaganda-video-1522985 |accessdate=2015-10-11 |agency=IBTimes UK |date=2015-10-08 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151011092445/http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/isis-child-jihadi-threatens-behead-president-obama-latest-propaganda-video-1522985 |archivedate=2015-10-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

截至2014年9月，有被伊斯蘭國控制的城市沒有興建任何[[學校|學校]]和[[大學|大學]]，該組織亦要求有意在其控制地區工作的教師必須先接受組織提供的課程<ref name=VICE />。

=== 對特定種族的迫害 ===
伊斯蘭國亦被指涉嫌干犯[[種族清洗|種族清洗]]罪行，迫害伊拉克北部等地的[[少數民族|少數民族]]，包括[[土庫曼人|土庫曼人]]、[[賽伯伊人|賽伯伊人]]、{{link-en|沙巴克人|Shabak}}等，迫害手法包括綁架和殺害這些族群的平民<ref>{{cite news |title=Iraq crisis: Islamic State accused of ethnic cleansing |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-29026491 |accessdate=2015-10-11 |agency=BBC |date=2014-09-02 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20140903160604/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-29026491 |archivedate=2014-09-03 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

